Odaily Planet Daily News: The overall market value of stablecoins increased by $7.7 billion in February, highlighting the rising demand for "digital dollars" in the crypto market. The main situation of the stablecoin market in February was: 
-USDS market value increased by 64%; 
-PYUSD market value increased by 49%; 
-USDT market value reached about $143 billion (an increase of $2.5 billion in February alone); 
-USDC market value increased by 7%. 
But in addition, the market value of USDe and DAI declined in February (News.Bitcoin).
